def maxProfit(prices):
    n = len(prices)
    if n < 2:
        return 0
    buy = -prices[0]
    sell = 0
    prev_sell = 0
    for i in range(1, n):
        tmp = sell
        sell = max(sell, buy + prices[i])
        buy = max(buy, prev_sell - prices[i])
        prev_sell = tmp
    return sell
